{"tid":302101,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打想學琴,樂理?","createTime":"2017-06-29T06:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T03:49:22.000Z","uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90bee9f7be16324b002c33ec3fd60528ebdca4ca","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:45:32.000Z","msg":"先利申下自己先<br />\n考左LT, AT, 8級琴+樂理<br />\n係香港國際音樂學校讀鋼琴教學<br />\n係幾個比賽拎過冠軍, 亞軍<br />\n(知我邊個拜託唔好起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n古典,流行, 點樣自己配CHORD, 樂理<br />\n初學 / 之前學過想再學 都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用三角琴上堂<br />\n收費當然係巴打價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家係到吹下水, 有咩問題會盡量解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7de8263a4090523a4652881f36155f57ae1e5e3","tid":302101,"uid":46209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"有興趣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78efecac87942cd24b6545effa49573f2b151834","tid":302101,"uid":45097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:53:33.000Z","msg":"幾錢同咩區？"},{"pid":"1e59a1f161e6d4876ae3dde10f30474278a5dc53","tid":302101,"uid":56111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢同咩區？</blockquote><br />\n留名 同問"},{"pid":"693427776972ea67a606022a07a5038664a99fea","tid":302101,"uid":88062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"巴打價啫係幾多？"},{"pid":"24d874c58df9c5bca0c4ec5e89d0fc01637ee089","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:09:06.000Z","msg":"Telegram:BCPiano<br />\nEmail: borispianomusic@gmail.com"},{"pid":"e350fce0fae11e5cd910bc272f6a2ff721c22b18","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾錢同咩區？</blockquote><br />\n留名 同問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n官塘區<br />\n有興趣email or telegram我<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de66dbe2db266d97d4fe665f9a16b07ef12a070","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打價啫係幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有興趣email or telegram我<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175317c5da76550d72516d124a4947b2adc1f201","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8846497171b3958cae07f39282768fbb5147bc","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:07:41.000Z","msg":"鳴呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea6567d74082ac43b1a7d259737c8bddead690b","tid":302101,"uid":107232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:49:24.000Z","msg":"想問8級樂理其實教到去邊<br />\n我個fd成日同我講8級樂理但我唔係跟嗰套系統學<br />\n唔知自己樂理程度放落去究竟算幾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f38b7cc1717a0f699c6d738ec356bfb47bf356","tid":302101,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:51:53.000Z","msg":"收幾錢"},{"pid":"7eb03d7b4550bd46079e4df956401eec6d5db46c","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問8級樂理其實教到去邊<br />\n我個fd成日同我講8級樂理但我唔係跟嗰套系統學<br />\n唔知自己樂理程度放落去究竟算幾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfigured bass(baroque trio sonata), harmonization(romantic piano work), chromatic alterations, nonchord tone, basic knowledge of orchestration, 仲有D 基本音樂分析, 咁上下"},{"pid":"59188b2b8c61598e712635dc85478217065a3725","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收幾錢</blockquote><br />\n有興趣請你<br />\nTelegram:BCPiano<br />\nEmail: borispianomusic@gmail.com<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0736bed1512f0995aab9f1ee3637e2daf7013cb","tid":302101,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:35:19.000Z","msg":"係就係到開價啦<br />\n搵食都咁唔見得光？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c421e273a53eeeb9f7b1c9deb694e9ffc278530","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係就係到開價啦<br />\n搵食都咁唔見得光？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係唔見得光, 但想有基本接觸姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外唔想發生不必要既罵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2a26c44eac91376d28ae751c97282964e39667","tid":302101,"uid":107232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問8級樂理其實教到去邊<br />\n我個fd成日同我講8級樂理但我唔係跟嗰套系統學<br />\n唔知自己樂理程度放落去究竟算幾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfigured bass(baroque trio sonata), harmonization(romantic piano work), chromatic alterations, nonchord tone, basic knowledge of orchestration, 仲有D 基本音樂分析, 咁上下</blockquote><br />\n咁我已經學曬有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近學緊12 tone tech <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懷疑緊人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb9690425cfba33d8fe185b0ff1c25ff2d7e9ff","tid":302101,"uid":42190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"有冇絕對音感"},{"pid":"1cc9b5e1e8f3ca5fb27dfdd8e73c952cfe7c8e23","tid":302101,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>收幾錢</blockquote><br />\n有興趣請你<br />\nTelegram:BCPiano<br />\nEmail: borispianomusic@gmail.com<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇到以為你講緊想講我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ad14362bdf744a63dbb8602aa0aea469f6e9aa","tid":302101,"uid":75116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"上門定點？"},{"pid":"fa61ff2e257ef9bec1224352878f454f3883a0c1","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問8級樂理其實教到去邊<br />\n我個fd成日同我講8級樂理但我唔係跟嗰套系統學<br />\n唔知自己樂理程度放落去究竟算幾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfigured bass(baroque trio sonata), harmonization(romantic piano work), chromatic alterations, nonchord tone, basic knowledge of orchestration, 仲有D 基本音樂分析, 咁上下</blockquote><br />\n咁我已經學曬有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近學緊12 tone tech <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懷疑緊人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n12 tone/serialism基本上毫無功能<br />\n除咗滿足班教授既淫威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇eric ewazen既作品 大多都係正常野"},{"pid":"cbeabf840a9a5b9899aa3d96bead4435e9e55b26","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇絕對音感</blockquote><br />\n冇, 基本上彈琴有relative pitch 就夠"},{"pid":"f3153bbd79e12cc75efa61476d3d21394892a280","tid":302101,"uid":107232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇絕對音感</blockquote><br />\n冇, 基本上彈琴有relative pitch 就夠</blockquote><br />\n絕對音感只會幫你做功課個陣快少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e2a5c06c064bcf5ae5e54f60e9bf6603df2f15","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上門定點？</blockquote><br />\n如果近可以上門, 但最好上我到學<br />\n因為上門會貴D 之外<br />\n我D 工具/教材準備得冇咁方便"},{"pid":"9f3c3c420cf2a4af7c9be20ed816d3137e353003","tid":302101,"uid":107232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問8級樂理其實教到去邊<br />\n我個fd成日同我講8級樂理但我唔係跟嗰套系統學<br />\n唔知自己樂理程度放落去究竟算幾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfigured bass(baroque trio sonata), harmonization(romantic piano work), chromatic alterations, nonchord tone, basic knowledge of orchestration, 仲有D 基本音樂分析, 咁上下</blockquote><br />\n咁我已經學曬有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近學緊12 tone tech <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懷疑緊人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n12 tone/serialism基本上毫無功能<br />\n除咗滿足班教授既淫威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇eric ewazen既作品 大多都係正常野</blockquote><br />\n聽左幾首<br />\n美國？定大勢？最近好似都係流行呢種風格<br />\n我上次去聽我老師吹拒自己原創曲都係咁既feel<br />\n我教授就話依家音樂處於一個復古時期，越來越多人批評無調"},{"pid":"1a0ff9368c8a26459a3881f2e8e32748d5557584","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇絕對音感</blockquote><br />\n冇, 基本上彈琴有relative pitch 就夠</blockquote><br />\n絕對音感只會幫你做功課個陣快少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唱歌 吹/拉 野就好有用<br />\n不過玩開lee 類既人後天都練到少少<br />\n但始終唔係天生個種咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有D 勁到一堆雜聲都聽到個pitch"},{"pid":"4ed4d776d83410dfe5b84de10dc2ea46c21c5922","tid":302101,"uid":107232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇絕對音感</blockquote><br />\n冇, 基本上彈琴有relative pitch 就夠</blockquote><br />\n絕對音感只會幫你做功課個陣快少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唱歌 吹/拉 野就好有用<br />\n不過玩開lee 類既人後天都練到少少<br />\n但始終唔係天生個種咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有D 勁到一堆雜聲都聽到個pitch</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我因為由細到大玩開in F既樂器搞到成日聽完要腦入面再轉多次調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁開口唱或者吹口哨就都算幾準<br />\n但人肉tuner個d真係做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de012ffe81eec2fe8fb933c7078cbd34f0b559ba","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問8級樂理其實教到去邊<br />\n我個fd成日同我講8級樂理但我唔係跟嗰套系統學<br />\n唔知自己樂理程度放落去究竟算幾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfigured bass(baroque trio sonata), harmonization(romantic piano work), chromatic alterations, nonchord tone, basic knowledge of orchestration, 仲有D 基本音樂分析, 咁上下</blockquote><br />\n咁我已經學曬有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近學緊12 tone tech <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懷疑緊人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n12 tone/serialism基本上毫無功能<br />\n除咗滿足班教授既淫威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇eric ewazen既作品 大多都係正常野</blockquote><br />\n聽左幾首<br />\n美國？定大勢？最近好似都係流行呢種風格<br />\n我上次去聽我老師吹拒自己原創曲都係咁既feel<br />\n我教授就話依家音樂處於一個復古時期，越來越多人批評無調</blockquote><br />\n我覺得(帶頭盔先) 係 大眾接受性/錢既問題<br />\n除左 電影會用泥做配樂, 平時都唔會有人鐘意聽<br />\n可能大家都慣咗tonal music, 一出世就已經慣咗, 形成左對音樂有種預期性, 所以冇咩市場<br />\n例如Bach 既作品, 過左200幾300年, 就咁受歡迎就知"},{"pid":"f5abccd81f93ffc72a1faf9ee72217b30d193cbe","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇絕對音感</blockquote><br />\n冇, 基本上彈琴有relative pitch 就夠</blockquote><br />\n絕對音感只會幫你做功課個陣快少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唱歌 吹/拉 野就好有用<br />\n不過玩開lee 類既人後天都練到少少<br />\n但始終唔係天生個種咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有D 勁到一堆雜聲都聽到個pitch</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我因為由細到大玩開in F既樂器搞到成日聽完要腦入面再轉多次調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁開口唱或者吹口哨就都算幾準<br />\n但人肉tuner個d真係做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n科技進步 電話都有tuner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 人肉tuner 除咗show off 都冇咩必要"},{"pid":"dc7f0dd45ba5f78b6a55c5771125b93c5f063478","tid":302101,"uid":107232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問8級樂理其實教到去邊<br />\n我個fd成日同我講8級樂理但我唔係跟嗰套系統學<br />\n唔知自己樂理程度放落去究竟算幾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfigured bass(baroque trio sonata), harmonization(romantic piano work), chromatic alterations, nonchord tone, basic knowledge of orchestration, 仲有D 基本音樂分析, 咁上下</blockquote><br />\n咁我已經學曬有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近學緊12 tone tech <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懷疑緊人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n12 tone/serialism基本上毫無功能<br />\n除咗滿足班教授既淫威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇eric ewazen既作品 大多都係正常野</blockquote><br />\n聽左幾首<br />\n美國？定大勢？最近好似都係流行呢種風格<br />\n我上次去聽我老師吹拒自己原創曲都係咁既feel<br />\n我教授就話依家音樂處於一個復古時期，越來越多人批評無調</blockquote><br />\n我覺得(帶頭盔先) 係 大眾接受性/錢既問題<br />\n除左 電影會用泥做配樂, 平時都唔會有人鐘意聽<br />\n可能大家都慣咗tonal music, 一出世就已經慣咗, 形成左對音樂有種預期性, 所以冇咩市場<br />\n例如Bach 既作品, 過左200幾300年, 就咁受歡迎就知</blockquote><br />\n我覺得有道理<br />\n得一小部分人識欣賞既音樂究竟仲算唔算好音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加上荷李活電影長期為音樂打標籤<br />\n令無調音樂比人一種係sound effect多過音樂既感覺"},{"pid":"1ed6ffe11acab8dd08770e7cc22850531c96970b","tid":302101,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"識唔識人教cello?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926889bbaf17080848043829be2fca1580609e69","tid":302101,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇絕對音感</blockquote><br />\n冇, 基本上彈琴有relative pitch 就夠</blockquote><br />\n絕對音感只會幫你做功課個陣快少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee0d975cb8336a2dfaf338483df769f5c6de774","tid":302101,"uid":13564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fad51ab45383ddb7cf7f9f76efdaa6b91c2c5536","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學但宜家份工就唔到時間練琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前叫學過3年嘅</blockquote><br />\n如果想學就一定要抽時間練<br />\n冇辨法, 想彈得好一定要每日抽少少時間練15mins 都好"},{"pid":"3cbf4cf7ca22b75b6bf327428968317269da9b5e","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問8級樂理其實教到去邊<br />\n我個fd成日同我講8級樂理但我唔係跟嗰套系統學<br />\n唔知自己樂理程度放落去究竟算幾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfigured bass(baroque trio sonata), harmonization(romantic piano work), chromatic alterations, nonchord tone, basic knowledge of orchestration, 仲有D 基本音樂分析, 咁上下</blockquote><br />\n咁我已經學曬有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近學緊12 tone tech <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懷疑緊人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n12 tone/serialism基本上毫無功能<br />\n除咗滿足班教授既淫威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇eric ewazen既作品 大多都係正常野</blockquote><br />\n聽左幾首<br />\n美國？定大勢？最近好似都係流行呢種風格<br />\n我上次去聽我老師吹拒自己原創曲都係咁既feel<br />\n我教授就話依家音樂處於一個復古時期，越來越多人批評無調</blockquote><br />\n我覺得(帶頭盔先) 係 大眾接受性/錢既問題<br />\n除左 電影會用泥做配樂, 平時都唔會有人鐘意聽<br />\n可能大家都慣咗tonal music, 一出世就已經慣咗, 形成左對音樂有種預期性, 所以冇咩市場<br />\n例如Bach 既作品, 過左200幾300年, 就咁受歡迎就知</blockquote><br />\n我覺得有道理<br />\n得一小部分人識欣賞既音樂究竟仲算唔算好音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加上荷李活電影長期為音樂打標籤<br />\n令無調音樂比人一種係sound effect多過音樂既感覺</blockquote><br />\nYeah! 如果12tone 係好野, 歷史會還佢一個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56910152740d9827a1bd69889f146610119ed704","tid":302101,"uid":65118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"想問下巴打學jazz piano 有冇心得可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學左dim/aug之類既scale但唔知應該點樣練熟佢地<br />\n利申廢jer得五級鋼同樂理底 好想學jazz piano<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b6bea68da0d6b4040e15c193bfa605fe32b896","tid":302101,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"香港國際音樂學校？ICQM？"},{"pid":"ceb2e9cb66687d111bc28cf3bf5f94b6512ef872","tid":302101,"uid":7678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"想問下jazz piano呀，請問有冇得教<br />\n本身考左鋼琴8級同樂理5級，8級樂理有學晒但係無考，黎緊想入中大音樂系同計劃緊考LT。<br />\n另外見巴打彈琴咁勁，有一事想請教。<br />\n我中四個陣彈琴傷到手，抖左兩年，CHECK到原因係正中神經受損，上年12月個陣好番啲，但係一彈耐啲都仲係手會刺痛同反應慢，感覺唔舒服，我想問會唔會係因為姿勢唔正確引致不斷番發?"},{"pid":"a69e7f30e6f398ba42812fcf7ed4aa950eba3fba","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下巴打學jazz piano 有冇心得可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學左dim/aug之類既scale但唔知應該點樣練熟佢地<br />\n利申廢jer得五級鋼同樂理底 好想學jazz piano<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJazz 都唔係我強項, 要比其他巴打解答<br />\n但可以講少少<br />\n首先jazz 有好多種風格, 主要係rhythm 既分別<br />\n主宰jazz 個種風格重要係rhythm, 所以音其實係其次<br />\nscale 如果想隨時用到,最好背晒佢, 彈arpeggios咁練"},{"pid":"f05961c2e147515aa6c24fbc409ee5e655812c76","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下jazz piano呀，請問有冇得教<br />\n本身考左鋼琴8級同樂理5級，8級樂理有學晒但係無考，黎緊想入中大音樂系同計劃緊考LT。<br />\n另外見巴打彈琴咁勁，有一事想請教。<br />\n我中四個陣彈琴傷到手，抖左兩年，CHECK到原因係正中神經受損，上年12月個陣好番啲，但係一彈耐啲都仲係手會刺痛同反應慢，感覺唔舒服，我想問會唔會係因為姿勢唔正確引致不斷番發?</blockquote><br />\n99% 姿勢唔正確 or 出錯力, 搵人執執佢好<br />\n如果唔係好快樽頸, 練極都上唔到去<br />\n基本上feel 到緊,累,痛就要休息, 唔好格硬黎, 然後檢視下自己出力方法<br />\n基本上彈琴用到個7個關節有冇理解各有咩功能?<br />\n我自己都係得Lt, 如果想考Lt 未必幫到你"},{"pid":"e891f4de8de103c22a63d766c89dee82ae159273","tid":302101,"uid":7678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下jazz piano呀，請問有冇得教<br />\n本身考左鋼琴8級同樂理5級，8級樂理有學晒但係無考，黎緊想入中大音樂系同計劃緊考LT。<br />\n另外見巴打彈琴咁勁，有一事想請教。<br />\n我中四個陣彈琴傷到手，抖左兩年，CHECK到原因係正中神經受損，上年12月個陣好番啲，但係一彈耐啲都仲係手會刺痛同反應慢，感覺唔舒服，我想問會唔會係因為姿勢唔正確引致不斷番發?</blockquote><br />\n99% 姿勢唔正確 or 出錯力, 搵人執執佢好<br />\n如果唔係好快樽頸, 練極都上唔到去<br />\n基本上feel 到緊,累,痛就要休息, 唔好格硬黎, 然後檢視下自己出力方法<br />\n基本上彈琴用到個7個關節有冇理解各有咩功能?<br />\n我自己都係得Lt, 如果想考Lt 未必幫到你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個鋼琴老師有同我汁姿勢，我自己都改左好多，但係都仲係會痛（睇痛得多定痛得小，無乜唔痛既時候），就唔知係咩問題。<br />\n我以前係用手指手腕力多，而家改左用臂力同身體既力多啲。<br />\n邊7個關節?求巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLT我會考係因為市場需要，但係其實我比較有興趣係流行音樂(特別係日本）同JAZZ，所以都想學下，ff緊做專業琴手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f05d78e0122f2ce3957c5085eaead5739a49eda","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下jazz piano呀，請問有冇得教<br />\n本身考左鋼琴8級同樂理5級，8級樂理有學晒但係無考，黎緊想入中大音樂系同計劃緊考LT。<br />\n另外見巴打彈琴咁勁，有一事想請教。<br />\n我中四個陣彈琴傷到手，抖左兩年，CHECK到原因係正中神經受損，上年12月個陣好番啲，但係一彈耐啲都仲係手會刺痛同反應慢，感覺唔舒服，我想問會唔會係因為姿勢唔正確引致不斷番發?</blockquote><br />\n99% 姿勢唔正確 or 出錯力, 搵人執執佢好<br />\n如果唔係好快樽頸, 練極都上唔到去<br />\n基本上feel 到緊,累,痛就要休息, 唔好格硬黎, 然後檢視下自己出力方法<br />\n基本上彈琴用到個7個關節有冇理解各有咩功能?<br />\n我自己都係得Lt, 如果想考Lt 未必幫到你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個鋼琴老師有同我汁姿勢，我自己都改左好多，但係都仲係會痛（睇痛得多定痛得小，無乜唔痛既時候），就唔知係咩問題。<br />\n我以前係用手指手腕力多，而家改左用臂力同身體既力多啲。<br />\n邊7個關節?求巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLT我會考係因為市場需要，但係其實我比較有興趣係流行音樂(特別係日本）同JAZZ，所以都想學下，ff緊做專業琴手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手指3個 手腕 手㬹 肩膊 腰<br />\n唔同聲音要唔同配合 組合"},{"pid":"4b541f4a08d3069f79f33a5a7d12f56c246fbe59","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港國際音樂學校？ICQM？</blockquote><br />\nicqm 係中小學部,唔同hkiim, 只係有部份設施共用"},{"pid":"11076b65dfe70ca07c99e0c75192eba271bd3b40","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a6098220ccc61caa8a502cd384cf88befc0bc4","tid":302101,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:32:21.000Z","msg":"屌 又r撈 好等錢洗咩"},{"pid":"1a7efcfbeb0d6d2636667238b923897fa96f8a40","tid":302101,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T0